			section 15;
			section 21;
			section 22, so far as relating to water or sewerage undertakers whose areasare wholly or mainly in England;
			section 25(3);
			sections 26 to 28;
			section 33;
			section 34(1) and (2);
			sections 35 and 36;
			section 57;
			section 58;
			section 60;
			sections 61 and 62 and Schedule 8;
			section 63;
			sections 85 to 87;
			section 88;
			section 89 and Schedule 10;
			paragraph 8 of Schedule 7 (and section 56 so far as relating to paragraph8);
			paragraph 107 of Schedule 7 (and section 56 so far as relating to paragraph107).
